text: There's a certain range for this, apparently.

So my team built an image processor where if you give it a plain text response or plain text description, we create vector art for slides, and you can even pass it along data, so it can automatically create a bunch of different figures for you, and then you're you can put that in.

So, the idea behind this product is that people who are building slides and reports all the time, we want to be able to save some of their time by letting them just explain the graphic they want and then automatically have one posted.
So this is a tool to help sales people, anyone doing reporting and slides, as well as saving designers time for initial inspiration.
So, yeah, that's what our product does.
